class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a5\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Буйруқ рақами</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a5\" style=\" margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#4}Буйруқ қабул қилинган жой</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">Ходимнинг иш жойини ўзгартириш тўғрисида</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">1. </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#6} Ходимнинг фамилияси, исми, отасининг исми</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\"> – </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#7}Ходим ишлаётган ташкилот номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#8}Ходимнинг лавозими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">ининг меҳнат шартномасида шарт қилиб кўрсатиб қўйилган иш жойи ходимнинг розилигига кўра </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#9}Ходим бошқа ишга ўтказилаётган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\"> кунидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#10}Ходим ўтказилаётган янги лавозим номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">га ўзгартирилсин ва шу кундан унинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#10}Ходим ўтказилаётган янги лавозим номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\"> сифатида меҳнат фаолиятининг давом эттириши белгилаб қўйилсин.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">2. Ходимнинг иш жойи ўзгартирилиши муносабати билан унинг аввалги иш жойидаги барча меҳнат кафолатлари ва имтиёзлари тўлиқ сақлаб қолинсин.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">Асос:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> Ўзбекистон Республикаси Меҳнат кодексининг 148–149-моддалари ҳамда меҳнат шартномасига ўзгартириш киритиш ҳақидаги келишув.</span></p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 203.50138504155px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#11}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг лавозими</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 188.21052631579px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">_________________</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 228.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">10_____________________</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>(имзо)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">Буйруқ реквизитлари:</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">1. Буйруқ қабул қилинган сана;</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">2. Буйруқ рақами;</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">3. Буйруқ қабул қилинган жой.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">Тарафлар:</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">4. Ходимнинг фамилияси, исми, отасининг исми;</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">5. Ходим ишлаётган ташкилот номи;</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">6. Ходимнинг лавозими; </span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">7. Ходим бошқа ишга ўтказилаётган сана;</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt;\">8. Ходим ўтказилаётган янги лавозим номи;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">9. Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг лавозими;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">10. Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг Ф.И.О.си.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n</div></div>",
